---
import CtaBtn from "./CtaBtn.astro"

const LinkText = encodeURI('Hola, quisiera conocer m√°s de sus servicios')
const WhatsAppNumber = `https://wa.me/573174048898?text=${LinkText}`
---
<main class="flex flex-col w-full h-dvh">
    <div class="main-container relative flex md:flex-row flex-col bg-white w-full h-dvh mt-25 md:mt-0">
        <div class="text-side flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-full md:w-[50%] md:h-full h-[50%] p-5 md:p-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col w-[90%] h-full justify-center items-baseline gap-y-4 md:gap-y-0">
                <h1 class="main-text flex justify-center md:items-end text-left text-main-orange md:leading-12 2xl:leading-18 text-4xl md:text-5xl 2xl:text-7xl font-[montserrat] font-bold animate-fade-in-down md:mb-12">Creemos en marcas que se recuerdan y dejan huella</h1>
                <div class="second-text md:w-[90%] text-left md:text-xl 2xl:text-4xl text-lg text-main-black font-[montserrat] animate-fade-in-down">
                    <p>Creamos marcas memorables y experiencias digitales que conectan con tu audiencia y hacen crecer tu negocio.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-side flex flex-col justify-between items-center md:w-[50%] w-full md:h-dvh h-[50%]">
            <div class="hero-cta flex flex-row justify-center items-center w-[90%] h-12 mt-10">
                <CtaBtn text="Ponte en contacto" link={WhatsAppNumber} variant="primary" responsive="flex md:hidden"/>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-char flex flex-row justify-around items-baseline w-full h-30 font-[montserrat] 2xl:mb-20 md:mb-5 mb-10">
                <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-[30%] h-[90%] p-2 md:p-4 text-lg md:text-md 2xl:text-2xl">
                    <span class="text-light-blue font-bold mb-2">100%</span>
                    <p class="text-center text-main-black">Clientes satisfechos</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-[30%] h-[90%] p-2 md:p-4 text-lg md:text-md 2xl:text-2xl">
                    <span class="text-light-blue font-bold mb-2">Alineados</span>
                    <p class="text-center text-main-black">con tus intereses y objetivos</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-[30%] h-[90%] p-2 md:p-4 text-lg md:text-md 2xl:text-2xl">
                    <span class="text-light-blue font-bold mb-2">Proceso</span>
                    <p class="text-center text-main-black">altamente colaborativo</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>